  "notes": [
    "Pinned OCI SDK contract: UpdateSecurityListDetails exposes defined_tags, display_name, egress_security_rules, freeform_tags, and ingress_security_rules as in-place updates; the handwritten runtime rejects create-only drift for compartment_id and vcn_id.",
